description:
As our customer numbers continue to grow, we are looking for a Business Development Manager based in Israel. We expect you to know the Israeli financial market like the back of your hand and understand the needs of local companies with cross-border business activity.

You’ll be tasked with establishing and strengthening relationships with new customers and building a network of partners locally.

Responsibilities:

Promoting MultiPass offering to potential customers and other financial institutions;
Seeking out and winning new customer relationships to drive revenue and margin growth;
Identifying new opportunities for growth;
Executing a plan based on the existing strategy, tailoring and refining it to convert prospects to customers;
Participating in conferences / expos on behalf of MultiPass.

Requirements:

Proven track record of business-2-business sales the designated geographical area;
Strong payments/banking industry background with an understanding of the payments ecosystem;
Experience across the industry;
Focus on new business development rather than account management;
Accountability mindset;
Flexibility for international travel.
Benefits:

Flexible working hours with great work-life balance;
Competitive compensation package including performance-related bonuses;
A perfect environment for professional growth and opportunities;
A friendly team of internationally based colleagues.Report
